      "post_id" : 7693999,
      "comment_id" : 62818385,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Note that this will not work for the <code>Integer</code> type, you will get a &quot;java.lang.Integer cannot be cast to java.lang.Character&quot; error. Add a cast to <code>int</code> first, e.g.:  <code>Character.toString((char)(int)myInteger);</code>"
