    "body" : "<p>This is an example, which shows that by converting an int to char, one can determine the corresponding character to an ASCII code.</p>\n\n<pre><code>public class sample6\n{\n    public static void main(String... asf)\n    {\n\n        for(int i =0; i&lt;256; i++)\n        {\n            System.out.println( i + \". \" + (char)i);\n        }\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
